name: Tie Belt Coat

name: Linen-blend Pants
description: Ankle-length pants in a woven linen and viscose blend. High waist, pleats at front of waistband, and elastic at back. Zip fly with button, diagonal side pockets, and mock welt back pockets. Tapered legs with creases.

name: Linen Joggers

name: A-line Skirt

name: Crinkled Skirt

name: Straw Bucket Bag

name: Nike Sportswear Essential
description: The Nike Sportswear Essential Women's Fleece Crew updates the classic comfort of semi-brushed fleece with raglan sleeves and ribbed details.

name: Nike F.C. Hoodie
description: The Nike F.C. Hoodie keeps you comfortable in football-inspired style made from soft fleece. Stretchy sleeve cuffs and an adjustable hood help hold in warmth from pitch to pavement.

name: Nike Air Hoodie
description: Made from soft fleece, the Nike Air Pullover Hoodie elevates a classic, comfortable look with contrasting graphics and premium details.

name: Jordan Jumpman
description: The Jordan Jumpman Jacket has you covered when the rain hits. Made with versatile fabric, it's got an adjustable hem and half-zip neckline for customisation. A wrap-around cut-and-sew panel adds distinction.

name: Nike Air Max 90
description: Nothing as fly, nothing as comfortable, nothing as proven—the Nike Air Max 90 stays true to its OG roots with the iconic Waffle sole, stitched overlays and classic TPU accents. Fresh colours give a modern look, while Max Air cushioning adds comfort to your journey.

name: Nike Air VaporMax 360
description: Inspired by heritage running shoes like the 2006 Air Max 360, the Nike Air VaporMax 360 re-imagines full-length Air with its lighter, more flexible design. The full-length foam midsole adds to the comfort while bold colours create a fresh, modern look.

name: Little Cropped Jacket
description: This is a cropped, button-front jacket with double patch pockets. It's made with textural, slightly structured basketweave fabric from Japan.

name: Palo Alto Teddy Jacket
description: This is a hooded teddy jacket with a cinchable shock cord at the waist and pockets lined with soft micro fleece. It's made with a soft, shaggy teddy fabric.

name: Renzo Pant
description: These are slim, tapered trousers with pleats along the front and back of the leg. They're made with stretchy crepe fabric from Japan.

name: Gables Tote Bag
description: This is an open woven tote with two shoulder straps. It’s made from 100% paper straw.

name: Classic Waistpack
description: This is a modern waist pack with polished hardware and an adjustable belt. It's made from smooth fabric with a glossy finish.

name: New Paperbag Pant
description: Pants that can do it all. These are wide-leg trousers with a high waist, a self-tie belt and a side-panel seam detail. They’re made with textural basketweave fabric from Japan.

name: Vito Linen Pant
description: These are high-rise, wide-leg trousers with crisp pleats and a straight waistband. They’re made with a blend of linen and TENCEL™ Lyocell — a wood-based fibre produced through a sustainable production process.

name: Troubadour Skirt
description: This is a flowy midi skirt with a smocked waist panel. It's made with lightweight, airy fabric.

name: Sculpt Knit Scallop Skirt
description: This is a high-waisted bodycon skirt finished with a scalloped hem. Babaton’s signature sculpt-knit yarn smooths and contours your shape

name: Lady Skirt
description: In this skirt. This is a high-rise, tiered skirt with embroidered trim and a high-low hem. It’s made with gauzy, organic cotton voile.

name: Sidonie Dress
description: This is a tiered mini dress with short flutter sleeves and a scalloped hem. It's made with lightweight modal fabric that drapes beautifully.

name: Aki Dress
description: This is a V-neck mini dress with a pointed collar, puff sleeves and a cinched elastic waist. It's made with fluid, flowy fabric. This version comes in a polka dot print that was designed in-house.

name: Jubilee Dress
description: This is a puff-sleeve, button-front dress with a low V-neckline and an empire waist. It's made with artisanal Broderie Anglaise fabric.

name: Mini Jute Bucket
description: This is a hand-woven bucket bag with a round base, drawcord closure and round resin handles. It's made with jute and has a 100% natural cotton liner. .

name: Leather Shopper Bag
description: This is a mini shopper bag with a leather cord handle and an adjustable, detachable shoulder strap. It's made from smooth, 100% genuine cow leather with a subtle texture.

name: Leather Shopper Bag
description: Better denim. Better planet. This pair of denim is part of our water-saving Washwell™ program. Compared to conventional wash methods, Washwell™ has saved millions of liters of water since 2016.

description: Gap was established in 1969 on Ocean Avenue in San Francisco, California. Our first store sold only denim and records. In celebration of our 50th anniversary, we have created this limited edition collection inspired by iconic vintage pieces from our archives.

name: NMD_R1 SHOES
description: Run with it. These adidas NMD_R1 Shoes are a little technical and a lot street smart. Their midsole plugs flash back to the '80s, but the knit upper, full-length cushioned midsole and EVA inserts are 100 percent fashion forward.
categories: men, women, unisex, shoes, sneakers, running

name: TANK DRESS
description: Hit refresh on your look in this tie-dyed tank dress. Keep your adidas style legit with signature 3-Stripes. Soft cotton jersey has a little stretch so you can dance if the mood strikes.

name: ADIDAS 3-STRIPES SKIRT
description: Techy? Sporty? Yes. Geek out about this chic 3-Stripes skirt. Put a futuristic spin on your look with ripstop pockets against a soft French terry backdrop. Style won.

name: OZWEEGO SHOES
description: When the adidas OZWEEGO Shoes were introduced as a running shoe back in the day, they opened the doors to a new future. Innovative. Daring. Technical. This iteration continues the legacy. Same progressive design. Same unparalleled cushioning. Though no running required this time.

name: STAN SMITH SHOES
description: Roll with the classic. Back in the day, Stan Smith won big on the tennis court. Slide into the adidas shoe worthy of his name and you'll win big on the streets. Top to bottom, these shoes capture the essential style of the 1971 original, with a minimalist leather build and clean trim.

name: SUPERSTAR SHOES
description: Originally made for basketball courts in the '70s. Celebrated by hip hop royalty in the '80s. The adidas Superstar shoe is now a lifestyle staple for streetwear enthusiasts. The world-famous shell toe feature remains, providing style and protection. Just like it did on the B-ball courts back in the day.    Now, whether at a festival or walking in the street you can enjoy yourself without the fear of being stepped on. The serrated 3-Stripes detail and adidas Superstar box logo adds OG authenticity to your look.

name: Journey Windbreaker
description: Designed for everyday adventures and long journeys, our Journey Windbreaker is a versatile style. This jacket packs away into a hood compartment with a hanger loop that clips onto your bag for on-the-go convenience. It features a zipper front, front pockets with snap closures, a drawcord hood and an elastic hem and cuffs.

name: Summerside Skirt
description: Perfect for the warmer weather, our Summerside Skirt is made with soft and lightweight baby french terry. This cozy style features a drawcord waist and our Cooper Beaver logo.

name: Womens Annex Cabin Slip On
description: Inspired by the Roots Cabin Collection, our Womens Annex Cabin Slip On features our signature cabin stripe detail. This slip-on style is designed with a full leather upper with an elastic gore, 100% cotton lining, a rubber outsole and a contoured PU footbed with a breathable foam top layer for comfort.

name: Mens Natural 2 Strap Sandal
description: Strap in and set off with our Natural 2-Strap Sandal, a Roots favourite featuring memory foam cushioning and a cored-out footbed for lightweight comfort.
